			<footer class="comment-meta">
				<div class="comment-author vcard">
					<img alt='' src='https://1.gravatar.com/avatar/44acef4a637da5c1e1328f67826eecae?s=39&#038;d=identicon&#038;r=R' class='avatar avatar-39' height='39' width='39' /><span class="fn"><a href='http://andrewgoldstone.com' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>Andrew Goldstone</a></span> on <a href="https://tedunderwood.com/2012/12/14/what-can-topic-models-of-pmla-teach-us-about-the-history-of-literary-scholarship/#comment-2774"><time datetime="2012-12-16T11:50:02+00:00">December 16, 2012 at 11:50 am</time></a> <span class="says">said:</span>
									</div><!-- .comment-author .vcard -->

				
