									</div><!-- .comment-author .vcard -->

				
			</footer>

			<div class="comment-content"><p>That being said, I very much agree with your point about it being time to use your eyes. The algorithms themselves are uncertain enough, and still incomplete proxies, that a difference of .2 in the r values really doesn&#8217;t say anything. It&#8217;s enough to point out something interesting and, as you&#8217;ve mentioned before, that&#8217;s when it&#8217;s time to start using your eyes and your brain to make more nuanced connections.</p>
</div>

