			<footer class="comment-meta">
				<div class="comment-author vcard">
					<img alt='' src='https://2.gravatar.com/avatar/e01704aab56a6abc54ecaa750f98e7b5?s=39&#038;d=identicon&#038;r=R' class='avatar avatar-39' height='39' width='39' /><span class="fn"><a href='http://new-savanna.blogspot.com/' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>Bill Benzon</a></span> on <a href="https://tedunderwood.com/2012/12/14/what-can-topic-models-of-pmla-teach-us-about-the-history-of-literary-scholarship/#comment-2739"><time datetime="2012-12-15T00:25:58+00:00">December 15, 2012 at 12:25 am</time></a> <span class="says">said:</span>
									</div><!-- .comment-author .vcard -->

				
