	<li class="comment even depth-3 highlander-comment" id="li-comment-2755">
		<article id="comment-2755" class="comment">
			<footer class="comment-meta">
				<div class="comment-author vcard">
					<img alt='' src='https://1.gravatar.com/avatar/17c1271b4f650c8cbe4f81d75a729cd7?s=39&#038;d=identicon&#038;r=R' class='avatar avatar-39' height='39' width='39' /><span class="fn"><a href='http://scottbot.net' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>Scott B. Weingart</a></span> on <a href="https://tedunderwood.com/2012/12/14/what-can-topic-models-of-pmla-teach-us-about-the-history-of-literary-scholarship/#comment-2755"><time datetime="2012-12-15T10:04:03+00:00">December 15, 2012 at 10:04 am</time></a> <span class="says">said:</span>
