			<div class="comment-content"><p>I spent time over the weekend writing a very long post centered on this work:</p>
<p>Literary History, the Future: Kemp Malone, Corpus Linguistics, Digital Archaeology, and Cultural Evolution</p>
<p>I’ve posted it at my personal blog:</p>
